    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introdução a Alien::Libxml2</title>

      <para>
        Alien::Libxml2 is designed to allow modules to install the C libxml2 library
on your system. In BLFS, it uses <command>pkg-config</command> to find how
to link to the installed <xref linkend="libxml2"/>.
      </para>

      &lfs113_checked;

